12. What: run validation and complete sign-off.
Why: confirm acceptance criteria and catch integration/regression issues before WORK phase.
How: run `tests/run-scenarios.sh gha-agent`, shellcheck on new script+SKILL and relevant files via `tests/run-scenarios.sh shellcheck`, then `ralph validate work`.
